# Viewing Pictures

Read this section for information on playback zoom and multi-frame playback.

Use the rear command dial to go from full-frame playback to playback zoom or multi-frame playback.

> Press **DISP/BACK** or **MENU/OK** to exit playback zoom or multi-frame playback and return to full-frame playback.

!Playback Controls

- **Full-frame playback**

  !Full-frame Playback

- **Multi-frame playback**

  - **Nine-frame view**

    !Nine-frame View

  - **Hundred-frame view**

    !Hundred-frame View

- **Playback zoom**

  - **Medium zoom**

    !Medium Zoom

  - **Maximum zoom**

    !Maximum Zoom
